SUBSTRATE   GTP [CPD:C00044]
PRODUCT     diphosphate [CPD:C00013];
            P1,P4-bis(5'-guanosyl) tetraphosphate [CPD:C01261]
COMMENT     Also acts, more slowly, on GDP to form P1,P3-bis(5'-guanosyl) triphosphate.
